snippet.title: Amber Heard is finally FIRED from Aquaman 2?!
snippet.description:
#AmberHeard #JohnnyDepp #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
Link to FRENCH TOAST VIDEO:  
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZYtvtHJqzls

Apparently Google is "confirmation" that Amber Heard has been fired from Aquaman 2. This is great insight but I don't think we can entirely confirm that Amber has officially been fired. I believe that it could happen but we will have to wait and see. I got my hopes up when I first saw this, but I think we still have to wait a bit until we find out for certain.
